{"tid":842612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲侍應嘅EQ幾高下","createTime":"2018-09-30T12:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T17:20:34.000Z","uid":180212,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd6586a057e435100fe78787bdb572b80996bee","tid":842612,"uid":180212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"岩係尖沙咀食嘢，有一男一女坐四人枱打橫坐，個侍應同佢地講話繁忙時間要打對坐，我見個餐廳又真係冇乜位，就算吉枱都係啲人啱啱走，之後見到個女嘅發脾氣，男嘅就寸個侍應話依家係繁忙時間咩？我見到有好多位喎<br />\n之後個侍應就答佢，八點幾係我哋餐飲業嘅繁忙時間，你依家可以打橫坐，不過你地咁坐，轉頭我地要入客嘅話要你郁就唔好，同埋位的確好多，不過全部都有人坐緊，如果你地中意打橫坐，不如安排個吧枱坐啊<br />\n之後，佢地柒住咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5e2307ea0fa6c3f724c21e52aadb072d9d02bb","tid":842612,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"咁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0845411a6e03bcb21a7f3678908ce9bc84c6ca29","tid":842612,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間唔係不嬲都2個坐一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d217b88d71f57f305729306d648202e3ba1a5","tid":842612,"uid":197998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0845411a6e03bcb21a7f3678908ce9bc84c6ca29","tid":842612,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間唔係不嬲都2個坐一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊卡位呀Ching"}]}